      <section eId="sec_CC-1423">
        <num>CC 1423</num>
        <heading>1423. Â Decedent's debts charged ratably</heading>
        <subsection eId="CC-1423__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Ratably to the fruits and products of property that is the object of general or universal legacies and of property that devolves by intestacy; and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CC-1423__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Ratably to the fruits and products of property that is the object of particular legacies, and then ratably to such property.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=108780</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
